note over browser:
/spa page already loaded
end note

note over browser:
User filles in input field
and clicks Save button
end note


note over browser:
onsubmit event is triggered and
callback function is called.
end note

note over browser:
Function adds new note to the list of notes.
end note

note over browser:
Function redraws all notes.
end note

note over browser:
Browser sends POST request to server.
end note

browser->server: HTTP POSTS https://fullstack-exampleapp.herokuapp.com/new_note_spa Content:{content: 'text', date: '2020-04-07T12:13:28.925Z'}

